        "Dear Sir or Madam,",
        "I am a member of your esteemed club and have been regularly enjoying the swimming activity. Although, last weekend, I faced an issue and would like to express my dissatisfaction with the same.",
        "I observed that the pool water is no longer pristine and has turned green. This concern could be due to the growth of algae in the pool area. Additionally, the whole experience of swimming was worst because it stinks in an area where the depth of water level is lesser. Moreover, I had rash all over my skin and felt itchy after diving inside.",
